data.description: Step into the welcoming embrace of 6321 Dartmouth Way! This stunning 6 bed, 3 bath home offers a generous 2400 square feet of living space, complete with a convenient double car garage. With fresh paint throughout, you'll feel the allure of a brand-new home. Enjoy the spacious backyard, complemented by a delightful screened-in porch offering relaxation and entertainment. The updated kitchen adds a touch of elegance to your culinary adventures. This impeccable residence is tailor-made for families yearning for utmost comfort, privacy, and contemporary living. Welcome to your dream home!
